==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pom-pom
<hw>Pom"-pom`</hw></mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Imitative.]</ety> <fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>originally,
a Vickers-Maxim one-pounder automatic machine cannon using metallic
ammunition fed from a lopped belt attached to the gun; -- popularly so
called from its peculiar drumming sound in action. More recently, the
term is applied mostly to automatic antiaircraft cannons.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pompom</ent>⟦br⟧
